thread.title: BRIEF-Pfizer Announces Tafamidis Phase 3 ATTR-ACT Study Met Its Primary Endpoint

title: BRIEF-Pfizer Announces Tafamidis Phase 3 ATTR-ACT Study Met Its Primary Endpoint

organizations.name: study met its primary endpoint reuters staff

text:
March 29, 2018 / 4:51 PM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Pfizer Announces Tafamidis Phase 3 ATTR-ACT Study Met Its Primary Endpoint Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
  Pfizer Inc: 
* PFIZER ANNOUNCES POSITIVE TOPLINE RESULTS FROM PHASE 3 ATTR-ACT STUDY OF TAFAMIDIS IN PATIENTS WITH TRANSTHYRETIN CARDIOMYOPATHY 
* PFIZER INC - STUDY MET ITS PRIMARY ENDPOINT 
* PFIZER INC - PRELIMINARY SAFETY DATA SHOWED THAT TAFAMIDIS WAS GENERALLY WELL TOLERATED 
* PFIZER INC - PRELIMINARY SAFETY DATA SHOWED THAT TAFAMIDIS WAS GENERALLY WELL TOLERATED IN POPULATION AND NO NEW SAFETY SIGNALS WERE IDENTIFIED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
